#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.7"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.7:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.7:0.2"
msgid "1. Bālavagga"
msgstr "1. Fools"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.7:0.3"
msgid "7. Sāvajjasutta"
msgstr "7. Blameworthy"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.7:1.1"
msgid "“Tīhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bālo veditabbo."
msgstr "“A fool is known by three things."

msgctxt "an3.7:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi tīhi?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.7:1.3"
msgid ""
"Sāvajjena kāyakammena, sāvajjena vacīkammena, sāvajjena manokammena … pe … "
"anavajjena kāyakammena, anavajjena vacīkammena, anavajjena manokammena … pe "
"…."
msgstr ""
"Blameworthy deeds by way of body, speech, and mind. … An astute person is "
"known by blameless deeds by way of body, speech, and mind. …”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.7:1.4"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
